<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Cougar Ridge</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">The Cougar Ridge real estate is a relatively young community and has been designed to cater to the needs of the active and busy lifestyles of young homeowners of today. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">A fine amalgamation of natural greenery and modern amenities, the Cougar homes for sale abound in different property types including town houses, single family homes, row houses, condos and what not.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The charming community boasts of a well planned architecture with a host of public amenities including shopping complexes, schools, recreational venues and playgrounds. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Some of the typical features of a Cougar Ridge home include open concept floor plans, hardwood flooring and vaulted ceilings.</p>
        </div>
